448
00:27:05,290 --> 00:27:07,080
-出版商  媒体  -我不知道
- Publishers, the press? - I don't know.

449
00:27:07,080 --> 00:27:08,640
那你知道什么
Well, what do you know?

450
00:27:09,940 --> 00:27:12,750
