You stay a million miles away from this.

454
00:27:26,980 --> 00:27:29,020
你怎么会这么蠢
How could you be so stupid...

455
00:27:31,530 --> 00:27:33,270
动了真情
to fall in love?

456
00:27:35,010 --> 00:27:36,490
这事还没提交表决
This thing isn't on the floor yet,

457
00:27:36,490 --> 00:27:37,510
我们就已经失去参议员的支持了
and we're losing senators.

458
00:27:37,510 --> 00:27:39,140
失去了几个吧  不过
We're losing some maybe, but...

459
00:27:40,430 --> 00:27:42,920
