I've done something unforgivable, LeAnn.

482
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:55,810
什么
What?

483
00:28:58,730 --> 00:29:00,390
我杀了佐伊·巴恩斯
I killed Zoe Barnes.

484
00:29:01,190 --> 00:29:02,910
