I won't be too long.

507
00:30:54,080 --> 00:30:55,100
你慢慢来
Take your time.

508
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,230
如果需要什么  我随叫随到
If you need anything, I'll be on call.

509
00:30:58,940 --> 00:31:00,060
