He said I wouldn't regret it... if I said yes.

523
00:32:07,850 --> 00:32:08,880
弗兰西斯
Francis.

524
00:32:09,560 --> 00:32:11,510
就是想当初  我同意
When I agreed to write the book

525
00:32:11,620 --> 00:32:14,070
写他起家的故事的时候
about his origin story way back when.

526
